Document: MeshInstance2D  
Path: godot/classes/class_meshinstance2d.rst  
Summary: Describes the mesh and texture properties for rendering in 2D with MeshInstance2D.  

Mesh (Mesh): The Mesh that will be drawn by the MeshInstance2D. Set via set_mesh(Mesh) and retrieved via get_mesh().  
Texture2D (Texture2D): The Texture2D used with the default CanvasItemMaterial. Accessible as TEXTURE in CanvasItem shaders. Set via set_texture(Texture2D) and retrieved via get_texture(). Note: This property is only relevant when using the default material.